<h2 style="font-size: 22px;">Fairmont State University</h2>
<strong>Fairmont, WV</strong>

<div class="infolines">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers credit for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers placement into higher-level courses for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>


<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Advanced placement and/or credit will be granted to students who have qualified on the basis of the tests of the Advanced Placement Program of the College Entrance Examinaton Board. Scores of three, four, or five are required.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.fairmontstate.edu/admit/applying-faqs" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

 <p class="box-padding-3">
    Additional restrictions and requirements may apply to the policy listed below. For more detailed information, visit the college's AP policy on the Web or contact the college directly.
